{"title":"坚决扫除非典病疫","authors":["启功"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决扫除非典病疫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"启功"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老鼠未过街，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欲打只能喊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瘟疫却无形，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"简名曰非典。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨起发高烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过午已发喘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄昏日落时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气塞不能缓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医者割喉咙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷秽全房满。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左右医护人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先后遭传染。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又或体温低，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞬息全身软。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不待求医生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已觉生命短。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天意重生民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百工各有术。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕种与庖厨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医疗兼看护。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医护服白衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神职天所赋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"病者一人疗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天使心同祝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"患者虽有增，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"市民心安宁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百货足日用，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行旅无留程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疫为百恶首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人为万物灵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄语告非典，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下终太平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公元二○○三年五月病目起草，时年九十。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}